                        <h3>🌾 AgriEcho – Offline AI Assistant for Farmers</h3>
                        <span class="project-status">Featured</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="project-description">
                        AgriEcho is an offline-first Progressive Web App (PWA) designed to empower farmers in rural areas with limited or no internet connectivity. It offers AI-powered crop support, disease detection, and agricultural tips—even when offline—through on-device machine learning, local storage, and periodic syncing.
                    </p>
                    <div class="project-tech">
                        <span class="tech-tag">HTML</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">CSS</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">JavaScript</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">EJS</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">Node.js</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">Express.js</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">MongoDB</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">IndexedDB</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">TensorFlow Lite</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">PWA</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">Service Workers</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag">AR.js/WebXR</span>
                    </div>
                    <strong>Key Features:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Crop Doctor AR: Augmented Reality-based plant disease detection using on-device TensorFlow Lite models</li>
                        <li>Voice and Text Chat Assistant for farming queries</li>
                        <li>Offline Capability: Full app functions even without the internet (Service Workers, IndexedDB, caching)</li>
                        <li>AgriTips Library: Offline-accessible tips on crop rotation, pest control, irrigation, etc.</li>
                        <li>SOS Alert Button: Emergency message sending when connected</li>
                        <li>Smart Sync: Syncs data with the cloud whenever internet is available</li>
                    </ul>
